1. How to book a service ?

 
you can follow below steps

 
1. search/select category 
2. book service. 
3. assigned professional will conact you and will come to your address

 
2. How to know f my request is confirmed ?

 
once you place a booking you will get a notificatio regarding your booking , alongwth this you will get a call from customer support team regarding your booking

 
3. when will the professonal reach for delivering service ?

 
Generally our professional reach on time for service , if professional is late in case, you can alway give a call on booking help number.

 
4. How to pay to the service ?

 
Currenlty we are accepting cash on delivery , soon we will be accepting online payement too.

 
5. Is there any service guarantee ?

 
If there is any damage made by professional, we are always here to help you out.
